==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fatherly
<hw>Fa"ther*ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Like a father in
affection and care; paternal; tender; protecting; careful.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>You have showed a tender, <qex>fatherly</qex> regard.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Of or pertaining to a father.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fathership</ent>⟦br⟧
